Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.35,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,那么 明天开始就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:40.07,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,高中二年级的暑假 说它能改变人一生也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:44.15,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,这个时候过度放纵 一旦失败会有何后果也不用我说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.95,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,不要被那些什么「人生多少次都可以重来」的鸡汤欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.52,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,为了让自己人生不留下遗憾 各位照顾好自己 下学期再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.17,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,小武那家伙 说话就不能再委婉一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.30,Default,Mika,0,500,0,,哎呀 一片惨淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:05.95,Default,Yukina,500,0,0,,别看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.52,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,火星的目标渐行渐远啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,外星人什么的最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.62,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,小剑 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.00,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,叫我剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:16.31,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.87,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,由希奈 不幸的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.15,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你英语成绩还不如剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.02,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,别总找别人老说古语的茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:32.97,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,这么一看 小剑生错了时代和地点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.72,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,Yes I can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:39.50,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,话说回来 总感觉学生变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.95,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,有些转学 有些回国了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.05,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,下学期估计更少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,为什么会输给区区剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.77,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你这肯定补习没跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不 不用补习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.60,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还要去黑部参加合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,说是要锻炼得自己能保护我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:02.52,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,原来如此 不过对由希奈而言总比补习要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.36,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,要是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.55,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,赤城 暑假你怎么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.30,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,不好意思 我有计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.20,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,嗯？ 去旅游什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.85,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,大概就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.12,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,听好了 你们这几个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:29.52,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,从现在开始一个月我要把你们重塑成真正的纯爷们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,请让我安静地做个温婉贤淑的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.37,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:34.55,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,请多关照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:35.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.10,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,那还有问吗 一起合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.62,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,让他尽可能接近驾驶员的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.35,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,你父亲还跟我说你就拜托给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.77,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,还说不需要手下留情 给我做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:51.90,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.27,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,回答是Sir yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.37,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.85,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,你这是什么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.42,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,Sir yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.52,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,大小姐完全没有必要接受如此训练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.15,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,没关系 赛巴斯酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.67,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,这是一个提高战术素养的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.65,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,而且最近身体有点缺乏锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:20.37,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,这夏天赞爆了 你们将以自由为代价体验到何为地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.60,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,哼 无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.62,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.52,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我可没兴趣陪你们搞这种无趣的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:37.47,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,这不是陆战队的训练 我也没有虐待女人小孩的趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.45,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,但是啊 剑 你另算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.82,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,体力的基础是心肺功能和持久力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.45,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,每天至少十五公里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.72,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,还剩十秒 加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.45,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.27,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,没事的 很快就会习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:29.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,索菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,神美姐 你要干嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.47,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.20,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,接下来才是正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:53.76,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,要做那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:54.87,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:56.97,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,感觉有什么反映
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.35,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,里面 身体的里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.77,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,神美的特技 以前我也体会过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.57,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,这样一来明天能舒服一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.55,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,对她还真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,啊 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,对哦 不在家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.42,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,Bonjour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.42,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.92,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,睡得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.07,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,感觉身体轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.50,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那个…先是跑步吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.65,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,你和剑要上课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:09.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.07,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,请问 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:19.18,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,武隅老师嘱咐我不要让你们疏于功课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,可没有老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.52,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,国语 数学 理科 社会 无论什么都包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:27.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.72,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,那么今天就到这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:39.07,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,明天是世界史 要把旧石器时代到工业革命一口气全部讲完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.40,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,同时不要忘记复习今天的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.87,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,十分钟后在射击场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:59.87,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,接下来向你们介绍一下一生的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这个难不成是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,眼力不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这算哪门子的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:13.27,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,日本政府接受了国联的要求 特别允许我们携带武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.12,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,说是用来防身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:16.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,索菲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:22.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:25.22,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,哦？ 在哪学的射击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.87,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,熟人那体验入队的时候稍微学过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:28.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:33.52,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,国家宪兵队治安介入部队 法国的反恐部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,哈…熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.97,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,下一个 白羽 你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.15,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:54.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.62,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,闭着眼睛是打不中靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我闭眼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.02,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,下一个轮到你了 剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.50,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我才不需要飞行道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.77,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,你就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.30,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.57,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,证明一下你刚刚说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:23.90,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,用户认证式的超震动刀吗 这刀造型还挺科幻的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.12,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这可是鬼所锻造的上等品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:29.77,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,不是这刀就不能斩断他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.15,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,哼 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.42,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,集中精神 下盘用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:58.50,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,视情况可能出现舍弃神器独自逃生的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:01.32,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,敌人可不只会出现在市区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.70,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sir yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:08.10,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,不要想别的 只看着自己脚下往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:20.25,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,全身大汉黏稠稠的 好想回家洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.57,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,好的 我就满足你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:33.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,救…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:37.05,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,实战中 机体也有可能会落水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.60,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,游上来 不然要淹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不行 太重了游不动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.35,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,冷静点 不要这种事就轻易认输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.50,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:12.07,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,干嘛呢 剑 不能太宠着她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.82,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,托姆 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.42,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了 机体出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是GAUS1还是2？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.80,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,机体运行第1237号实验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:58.75,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,根据重力控制拓展功能与液相互作用实现的步行功能以及水密性的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.32,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,简单地说就是水遁术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:06.55,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,话说回来 没想到这边的日程竟会提前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.50,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,有意见去找托姆去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:13.12,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,陆战队没教过水容易导电吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:18.77,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,不过也正因如此 剑他们有了意料之外的休息时间 现在应该挺开心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.17,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,赤城先生 准备如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边随时就可以开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.20,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,感觉自己像动物园的猴子一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:38.55,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,自作自受 谁让你想都没想就启动了剑的项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:39.70,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,托姆 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:42.75,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 犬子的事真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是真的 那个…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:57.40,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,你没必要道歉 你应该庆幸他在受重伤之前就退出了训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.05,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,要放弃的话还是趁早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.77,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,我 绝对 不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.85,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,水池触电的时候我还以为要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.40,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,不过也因此有了1天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.30,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,真是歪打正着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs45}摘取项圈的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:26.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,如果这个实验成功了的话 GAUS也能像敌人那样在水上行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.22,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,要是能顺利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.25,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,美夏现在在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.37,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,应该在享受暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.80,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,荻布同学的话 我在网上看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.62,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这是什么打扮 不知廉耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,何塞 在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真好 你女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:10.80,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么这个点就回来了 不要上班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,GAUS要搞实验 挖掘队那边放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现场的保安等级也提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,其实爸爸我也看到外星人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.42,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,那你还真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,NO 好歹也对爸爸感点兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.20,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,GAUS1向控制台报告 重力控制没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,了解GAUS1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把绳索放松一些 你试着走几步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.57,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止游客使用无人机器人进行拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍 禁止游客使用无人机器人进行拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:18.47,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,同样角度的拍摄哪会有点击量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.72,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,感觉不错 这样不管什么样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.40,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.42,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,重力控制系统宕机 本机正在沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.85,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,混蛋 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.35,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,喂 该死的 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.27,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,控制台 这里是GAUS1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:57.40,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,驾驶舱出现漏水 望尽快进行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.32,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,防水性也是一个课题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.30,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,摘除青马剑之介的电击项圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:10.60,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,嗯 剑之介他救了由希奈好几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.05,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,那东西已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.75,Default,Heath,0,0,0,,我们仍会保持对他的监视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.35,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,那是一码事 这是另一码事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.25,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,暑假马上就要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:35.77,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,嗯 你的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.97,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,他们说你可以拿着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:51.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我先说好 这可不是让你去死的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.37,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.67,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这个好像也不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.22,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:10.12,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:14.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我在想电击有没有留下什么疤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.57,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.57,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:50.36,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}誰も皆 孤独なStray Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:53.06,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}授かった その名前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:22:01.12,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}片切符(かたきっぷ)に 時を 渡るの
